      "MegaPoisonPloyALokiRegular": {
        "id": "MegaPoisonPloyALokiRegular",
        "found": true,
        "localization": {
          "name": "Dark Hypnosis",
          "description": "Hypnotizes a random enemy (20%+ chance) and Mega Poisons them for 200TU (100% chance). A Hypnotized enemy will use its next turn to grant the turn to and Purify the hypnotizer (the turn will be lost as if it were sleeping), and then the hypnosis will end. The chance of Hypnosis applying increases by 20% for each awakening the user has, up to 100% max when fully awakened.\n\nHypnosis is not a status effect and cannot be removed by Purify skills, but will be canceled if the user is defeated or leaves the battlefield. Mega Poison will overwrite other status effects on that enemy. Mega Poison deals 20 times the damage of normal Poison and cannot be overwritten by normal Poison or Super Poison.\n\nThis skill becomes locked for 100TU after use and cannot be used if an enemy is already Hypnotized. Hypnosis will fail against Boss units.",
          "selected": "Mega Poison a random enemy, chance of Hypnosis\n(Will overwrite other status effects)"
        },
